&lt;li&gt;Present design reviews, run analysis, visit vendors, design &amp;amp; execute hardware test plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use first principles physics as a basis for every decision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get exposure to missile integration and testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel to test sites and vendors as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
