&lt;li&gt;3 months - 2 years of technical work to include technical internship and able to start full time in 2026.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated hands-on fabrication or laboratory skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CAD skills (any platform) and ability to make high quality engineering drawings that meet common industry standards.&lt;/li&gt;
