&lt;li&gt;Experience operating within a global organizational structure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Excel skills and proficiency with ERP systems (Oracle Fusion or another large ERP system preferred).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent stakeholder management and interpersonal skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven analytical and problem-solving skills with a mindset for continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
