&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;text-start &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead MDAO Initiatives:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with air-vehicle design and analysis disciplines and technical leadership across AD&amp;amp;S programs to define and execute critical trade studies, building robust, data-driven workflows using commercial MDAO frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
